1.title: Episode #4.1

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: Charlie Pickering, Tom Gleeson, Kitty Flanagan, Adam Briggs and special guest Celia Pacquola tackle killer robots, school reforms, the Royal Commission, and more. Tom Hard Chats Em Rusciano.

2.title: Episode #4.2

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

2.plot: Laugh along as Charlie Pickering, Tom Gleeson, Kitty Flanagan and Adam Briggs dig beneath the week's headlines and attempt to figure out what is going on, who is running it, and how to make it stop.

3.title: Episode #4.3

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

3.plot: Dissecting the week's headlines, Charlie puts NAPLAN to the test, Briggs puts Bill Shorten to the test, Kitty tests bottled water, Tom tests Amanda Keller on Hard Chat, and royal wedding coverage tests everybody.

4.title: Episode #4.4

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

4.plot: The Weekly eyeballs the Royal Wedding, white powder in Parliament, Yanny or Laurel, and why teeth aren't covered by Medicare. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats Andrew Denton. Special guests: Missy Higgins and comedian Alex Edelman.

5.title: Episode #4.5

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

5.plot: The Weekly team interrogates Barnaby Joyce, defends the Shoey, and salutes rural journalism. Kitty Flanagan tries hotdesking, Tom Gleeson Hard Chats Todd Sampson, plus Randy is our surprise NY correspondent.

6.title: Episode #4.6

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

6.plot: The Weekly probes match-fixing in schools, fake deaths, Barnaby and Vikki's tell-all interview, and political correctness gone mad. Tom Gleeson takes on the entire city of Launceston. Special guest: Tina Arena.

7.title: Episode #4.7

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

7.plot: The Weekly's newshounds sniff out the laughs in high-powered summits, Love Island, and poo joggers. Tom hard chats Adam Gilchrist, Kitty tries kombucha, and Roy Slaven and HG Nelson preview the World Cup.

8.title: Episode #4.8

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

8.plot: The Weekly tackles Optus's World Cup woes, Clive Palmer's return, baby formula wars and an ABC sell-off. Kitty Flanagan road-tests hit game Fortnite. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats MP Tim Wilson. Special guest: Guy Pearce.

9.title: Episode #4.9

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

9.plot: The Weekly takes on the plastic bag ban, tax cut coverage, Koko the gorilla, Logie nominees and Putin's World Cup. Kitty Flanagan has tax-time tips. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats Grant Denyer. Guest: Sally Pearson.

10.title: Episode #4.10

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

10.plot: The Weekly tees off on the Senate showdown, the Basketbrawl, Bill Shorten's back-flip and a Logies insurgency. Kitty Flanagan takes on bag rage. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats comedian Fiona O'Loughlin. Guest: Eddie Perfect.

15.title: Episode #4.15

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

15.plot: Charlie quizzes Barnaby Joyce, Tom Hard Chats Sarah Harris, Kitty presents her Rules for Life. We probe Barrier Reef funding, Wiggles wobbles, footy king-hits, ASIC spying on banks plus Woolies spying on you.

16.title: Episode #4.16

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

16.plot: Space Force, the horse who won't race, Senator Anning's phrases, and why power bills really went up. Denise Scott fixes the Oscars and Tom Gleeson takes his show Go Away to Melbourne. Special guest: Eddie Izzard.

18.title: Episode #4.18

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

18.plot: Charlie dissects the leadership spill and studies 'studies', Kitty Flanagan solves children's parties, Briggs interviews Simpsons creator Matt Groening, and Tom Hard Chats Human Nature.

19.title: Episode #4.19

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

19.plot: The Weekly investigates Mad Monday, bad honey, and lab-grown meat. Kitty Flanagan fixes superannuation. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats Roxy Jacenko. Roy and HG preview footy finals and hail Australia's newest hero, that tennis guy.

20.title: Episode 20

episode of.title: The Weekly with Charlie Pickering (TV Series 2015– )

20.plot: The Weekly picks apart Serena's serve, opioid addiction, and the Muppets in Canberra. Tom Gleeson Hard Chats music legend Paul Kelly. Kitty Flanagan rests in peace. Special Guest: Olivia Newton-John (Season Final)
